{
  "stem": "14156.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The cooking was done on Friday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there was a special kugel they're called, potato kugel or whatever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it was put on Friday night in the oven.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And kept-- the coals kept warm all through the night until the next day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So we did not have to light up anything like the coals or anything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We just took it out and served it on the table, without doing anything wrong.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And when they came to Saturday night, when the week was over, and what I don't forget-- [CRYING] My grandmother always blessed me like this.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She had a, she had a candle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was twisted, with a lot of colors on it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And she took, she took a little dish, poured wine in it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the candle was lit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then she put the candle into the wine and lit it-- I mean, and extinguished it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then she said, well-- how they say-- have a good week.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[HEBREW], they say that in Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- you know, this still goes with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SOBBING] Sometimes I feel that this helped me in life to stay on the earth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you mean-- well, we had Passover, there was Hanukkah, there was, there was Yom Kippur and, and Rosh Hashanah, naturally.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We observed that very, very much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On Rosh Hashanah we all had went to the temple, to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on Yom Kippur, nobody ate nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That means-- I was the only child.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Until my Bar Mitzvah, I could go along with a half a day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "After a half a day, they sent me home and said, OK, you can go home.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There's something to eat there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You're OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I will not forget, a year before my Bar Mitzvah, I was told to fast a whole day.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
